             <p><b>a. Scope of Services for E-Invoice GSP API Integration Consultation</b></p>
                     <ol style="list-style-type: lower-roman;">
                        <li> Cleartax shall provide technical documentation on APIs exposed.</li>
                        <li> Cleartax shall provide consultation on technical feasibility and data sufficiency from the API perspective to enable speedy execution and completion for the customer.</li>
                        <li> All the E-invoicing APIs provided by GSTN/NIC to Cleartax as the GSP shall be further released in the same form and quantum as may be provided to it by GSTN/NIC. The GSP shall not discriminate or show bias or give preferential treatment, directly or indirectly, in sharing of the aforesaid APIs.</li>
                        <li> Cleartax as a GSP will expose relevant APIs to the customer and shall generate sub-license key for authenticating to the GSTN/NIC server and for encryption and decryption of the data from and to the GSTN/NIC server.</li>
